10
00:00:28,180 --> 00:00:28,680
Retrofitting.

11
00:00:28,700 --> 00:00:33,684
So basically, I always say, and I tell people this over and over, you should always consider

12
00:00:33,744 --> 00:00:35,765
accessibility from the very beginning of a project.

13
00:00:36,465 --> 00:00:38,027
But what happens when you don't?

14
